settings.description:
Back-trek your way to secrets, special coins, and warps!

--Intended with any character--
--A redesign of Back-Tracking Bonanza--
Just a simple traditional level with note blocks, try to find all 5 e-Coins!

Please play on Christmas it will be amazing.
Follow BJuned with his new youtube channel at: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GAEoQjHK2lA&t=3s

Solve puzzles, fill in empty spaces, set record time .. and play sudoku. Except it isn't sudoku? I'm baffled at what it's called. 

Hint: Make sure not to have a starman while getting a goomba's shoe.
wow the jellyfish are flying. theres also a coin above the item slot machine in the 2nd room.
This is the third part of the series that makes us giggle the most while we lose. This is a level with a lot of trolling, something that is no longer funny but sad
